title: Ryan gets supermajority of House Freedom Caucus' support for speaker, but not full endorsement
text: Wisconsin Rep. Paul Ryan gained support from a key group Wednesday night for House speaker when a supermajority of the House Freedom Caucus announced it was backing him. ...
